reviewText: Very little moves with amateur like performers. This dvd is neither fun nor can it be classified as a workout. Total runtime is only 24 minutes and it cost around $17. Very disappointing, buyers beware of this product!

I have new respect for dancers.  Some of the moves seem like no big deal or pretty easy, but were great for the legs and body.  I really enjoyed this.  Taps into my sexy side and makes me really love my body.  Goes by fast.  She goes over the moves several times, has a good pace, speaks to you like you're there and not like you're a total idiot (like some dance dvds).
